titleInfo.title: Christian Brothers College Reception to our Bishop, Right Reverend Joseph Rademacher: Eighteenth Anniversary of the Opening of the College

mods.abstract: Bishop of Nashville, the Right Reverend Joseph Rademacher attended the 18th anniversary celebration of the founding of Christian Brothers College in November 1889.
